divs: Sighting DetailsI was in a vacation in Lisbon and in 19 september 2010 I made a trip to Sintra. I took this picture from a balcony from Sintra Pacace. The strange thing was that I didn't see anything with my eyes, only later, in the evening, when I reviewed all photos in that day.
